title: Wholesale Price of Lard for New York, NY
notes:
Series Has Been Subdivided Into Two Variables: (1)-- Original Data, 1911-1944; (2)--Original Data, 1938-1956. Data Is The Average Of Range Of Prices On Tuesday Of Each Week. Source: Bls Bulletins And Monthly Issues Of "Wholesale Prices"

This NBER data series m04026a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 4 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter04.html.
